OL,3,CThe little plant that's helping save
OL,4,Cthe planet
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Correspondent Mel
OL,7,FBarham went to find out why volunteers
OL,8,Fare helping to plant thousands of
OL,9,Fsphagnum moss on the West Pennine
OL,10,FMoors.
OL,12,FA team of volunteers have been helping
OL,13,Fto plant thousands of sphagnum moss on
OL,14,Fthe West Pennine moors, in a bid to
OL,15,Fhelp restore vital peatlands.
OL,17,FSphagnum moss can hold 20 times its
OL,18,Fweight in water and helps create peat
OL,19,Fbogs, capturing carbon in the ground
OL,20,Fand helping to fight climate change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
