OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774469469
OL,3,CThe little plant that's helping save
OL,4,Cthe planet
OL,6,FThe Lancashire Peat Partnership,
OL,7,Fhosted by the Lancashire Wildlife
OL,8,FTrust, has been working on a 28-
OL,9,Fhectare area of blanket bog on the
OL,10,Fedge of Hoddlesden Moor, which was a
OL,11,Fformer peat extraction site.
OL,13,FThe moss is a vital part of the peat
OL,14,Fbog restoration, which also helps
OL,15,Freduce flooding and moorland fires.
OL,17,FSince August, around a hundred
OL,18,Fvolunteers from across Lancashire have
OL,19,Fbeen helping to plant the moss on the
OL,20,Fsite at Aushaw Moss near Darwen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
