OL,3,CThe little plant that's helping save
OL,4,Cthe planet
OL,6,FWhat is Sphagnum Moss and why is it so
OL,7,Fimportant for the climate?
OL,9,FSphagnum Moss is a small but mighty
OL,10,Fplant. Not the type of moss found in
OL,11,Fgardens, Sphagnum moss is only found
OL,12,Fin wet acidic areas such as peatlands,
OL,13,Fin fact it creates the peat itself.
OL,15,FAs peat forms from only partially
OL,16,Fdecomposed plant matter it means that
OL,17,Fthe carbon that has been absorbed by
OL,18,Fthe plants through photosynthesis
OL,19,Fbecomes trapped in the peat, and
OL,20,Flocked away for millennia.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
