CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774469469
OL,3,CThe little plant that's helping save
OL,4,Cthe planet
OL,6,FMuch of our peatlands have been
OL,7,Fdamaged by draining them to make way
OL,8,Ffor farming and forestry, and by
OL,9,Fextracting peat for use as fuel and
OL,10,Fcompost.
OL,12,FRoughly 80% of England's peatlands are
OL,13,Fin a dry and degraded state, which is
OL,14,Fa problem because instead of acting as
OL,15,Fa carbon store, they actually become a
OL,16,Fcarbon emitter - releasing carbon
OL,17,Fdioxide back into the atmosphere and
OL,18,Fcontributing to climate change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
