PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774469469
OL,3,CThe little plant that's helping save
OL,4,Cthe planet
OL,6,FThe Wildlife Trust says at least 4% of
OL,7,Fall UK greenhouse gas emissions come
OL,8,Ffrom degraded peatlands.
OL,10,FRestoring (rewetting) fixes water
OL,11,Flevels to halt decomposition, reduces
OL,12,Fflood risks, improves water quality,
OL,13,Fand restores biodiversity.
OL,15,FHow can sphagnum moss help alleviate
OL,16,Fflooding?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
